Haralick texture features
-------------------------

https://www.orfeo-toolbox.org//doxygen/classotb_1_1ScalarImageToTexturesFilter.html


build on 12.04 ubuntu

with otb version 4.2.0

cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -DOTB_USE_EXTERNAL_LIBKML=ON -DBUILD_APPLICATIONS=OFF -DBUILD_EXAMPLES=OFF -DBUILD_TESTING=OFF -DCMAKE_VERBOSE_MAKEFILE=ON -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$OTB_HOME ../OTB-4.2.0

